title: D-A-D - The Overmuch Box - 12 CD-BOX 2009
description:
D-A-D is a Danish rock band known as Disneyland After Dark, a name that had to be changed after a threatening lawsuit from The Walt Disney Company. Their style of music is often categorized as melodic heavy rock. 

The Overmuch Box celebrates the 25 years of D-A-D and was released on November 16th, 2009. It is a release of their complete studio works up to 2009, containing 10 remastered studio albums plus rarities. However, the set does not include the band's live material. (wikipedia.org)
